nodes.text: Rayne Roberts is a creative executive for Lucasfilm Ltd. and member of the Lucasfilm Story Group. She was involved in the production of Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens, Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, Star Wars: Episode VIII The Last Jedi, Solo: A Star Wars Story, Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker, and the animated series Star Wars Rebels. Along with Leslye Headland, she will co-develop the upcoming television series Star Wars: The Acolyte.
